citation: Government Prices Oversight (MAIB Premiums) Amendment Order (No. 2) 2010 (Tas)
text:
Government Prices Oversight (MAIB Premiums) Amendment Order (No. 2) 2010

I make the following order under section 36 of the Economic Regulator Act 2009 .

8 September 2010

LARA GIDDINGS

Minister for Infrastructure

1. Short title
    This order may be cited as the Government Prices Oversight (MAIB Premiums) Amendment Order (No. 2) 2010 .

2. Commencement
    This order takes effect 61 days after the day on which its making is notified in the Gazette.

3. Principal Order
    In this order, the Government Prices Oversight (MAIB Premiums) Order 2009 is referred to as the Principal Order.

4.
    The amendment effected by this clause has been incorporated into the authorised version of the Government Prices Oversight (MAIB Premiums) Order 2009 .

5. Legislation revoked
    The legislation specified in Schedule 1 is revoked.

SCHEDULE 1 - Legislation revoked

Clause 5

Government Prices Oversight (MAIB Premiums) Amendment Order 2010 (No. 76 of 2010)
                                                                                 


Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 15 September 2010

This order is administered in the Department of Infrastructure, Energy and Resources.
